* {{ill|Kalpina|ja|劫賓那|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kalpina|qq=}} - A disciple of [[:en:The Buddha|Shakyamuni]]. * {{ill|Kumbhīra|ja|宮比羅|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kumbhīra|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} - The chief deity among the [[:en:Twelve Heavenly Generals|Twelve Heavenly Generals]] of [[:en:Bhaisajyaguru|Yakushi Nyorai Medicine Buddha]]. * [[:en:Konpira Gongen|Konpira Gongen]] - A syncretic deity from Japan's Shinto-Buddhist fusion, known during the medieval and early modern periods as "Konpira-sama" or "Konpira-san." * [[:en:Kotohira-gū|Kotohira-gū]] - The head shrine of post-Meiji "Konpira" worship, enshrining the Shinto deity Ōmononushi. It is a [[:en:Beppyo shrine|Beppyo Shrine]] managed by the religious corporation {{ill|Kotohira Hongyō|ja|金刀比羅本教|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kotohira Hongyō|qq=}}.
